						<h1 id="firstHeading">Prentice Hall</h1>			
<table class="infobox vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<caption class="fn org" style="">Prentice Hall</caption>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:LogoPrentice.jpg" class="image"><img alt="LogoPrentice.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a1/LogoPrentice.jpg/250px-LogoPrentice.jpg" width="250" height="159" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a1/LogoPrentice.jpg/375px-LogoPrentice.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a1/LogoPrentice.jpg/500px-LogoPrentice.jpg 2x"></a></td>
